org.concordion.cubano.driver.web

Class Browser

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.concordion.cubano.driver.web.Browser

  • public class Browser
extends java.lang.Object

    A wrapper around Selenium WebDriver to make it easier to open and close a specific browser regardless of whether that browser is running locally or remotely.
